==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Enregister
<hw>En*reg"is*ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>en-</ets> + <ets>register</ets>: cf. F. <ets>enregistrer</ets>. Cf.
<er>Inregister</er>.]</ety> <def>To register; to enroll or record; to
inregister.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>To read <qex>enregistered</qex> in every nook⟦br⟧
His goodness, which His beauty doth declare.</q>
<rj><qau>Spenser.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Enrheum</ent>⟦br⟧
